    <item>
      <title>无论是哈里斯还是特朗普，美国都必须避免新一轮核军备竞赛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-07-31/harris-or-trump-the-us-must-avert-a-new-nuclear-arms-race-with-russia-and-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[下一任总统将面临新的危险，即两大核对手中国和俄罗斯联手。但这并不意味着美国需要更多核武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-07-31/harris-or-trump-the-us-must-avert-a-new-nuclear-arms-race-with-russia-and-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
